hadiths[10]{hadithnumber,text}:
2502,"Hazrat Abdullah bin shikhkhir Aamiri (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai, Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : momin ka gum shuda janwer (jahannam ki) aag ka shola hai."
2503,"Hazrat munzir bin Jareer (Rahimahullah) sey riwayat hai, unhoney farmaya : main maqam Bawazij par apney walid (Hazrat Jareer bin Abdullah bijli (Raziallahu anhu)) key sath tha ke gayen (charagaah sey wapis) ayen. unhen (rewad mein) eik gaey nazar aai jo unhen ajnabi mehsus hui ( mehsus huwa ke hamari nahin) to unhoney farmaya : ye kaisi gaey hai? haazirin ney kaha : (kisi ki) gaey (hamari) gaayon key sath mil kar aa gaee hai. Hazrat Jareer (Raziallahu anhu) key hukm sey us ko haank diya gaya yahan tak key wo nazron sey ojhal ho gaee , phir unhoney kaha : mainey Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) sey suna hai, aap ney farmaya : bhatkey huye ( gum shuda) janwer ko (apney rewad mein) wohi jagah deta hai jo bhatka huwa ( gumrah) hai."
2504,"Hazrat Zaid bin Khalid johni (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai, unhoney Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) sey riwayat kartey huye farmaya ke aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) sey gum shuda oont key barey mein daryaft kya gaya to aap naraz ho gaey aur aap key rukhsaar Mubarak ( ghussey sey) surkh ho gaey aur farmaya : tujhey us sey kya gharz? uskey paas jootey bhi hain aur mashk bhi. wo pani ( key chashmon) par jaeyga (aur pani pi liya kerega) aur darakhton key pattey khata rahega yahan tak key uska Malik us tak pahunch jaey. Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) sey gum shuda bakri key barey mein puchha gaya to aap ney farmaya : usey pakad ley . wo teri hai ya terey bhai ki ya bhediye ki. aur Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) sey giri padi chiz key barey mein sawal kya gaya to aap ney farmaya : uski thaili ko aur bandhan ko pehchan ley, aur eik saal tak uska aelan kar, agar koi usey pehchan ley (to behtar hai) warna usey apney maal mein mila ley."
2505,"Hazrat ayaaz bin himaar (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai, Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : jis shakhs ko kisi ki gum shuda chiz miley to usey chahiye ke eik ya do moatabar aadmiyon ko gawah bana ley . phir is mein tabdili na karey aur na usey chupaey. iskey baad agar uska Malik aa jaey to wo (Malik) uska ziyada haq daar hai warna wo Allah ka maal hai jisey wo chahta hai, dey deta hai."
2506,"Hazrat Suwed bin Ghafala (Rahimahullah) sey riwayat hai, unhoney farmaya : main Hazrat Zaid bin Sohaan aur Hazrat Salman bin Rabeea (Rahimahullah) key sath safar par rawana huwa . jab hum maqam Uzeb par pahunchey to mujhey kisi ka gira huwa koda mila. un dono hazraat ney kaha : usey phenk do . mainey ( phainkney sey) inkar kar diya . jab hum Madina Munawra pahunchey to mainey Hazrat Ubai-bin Kaab (Raziallahu anhu) ki khidmat mein hazir ho kar waqia bayan kya (taake masla malum ho jaey ( unhoney farmaya : tu ney sahih kya. Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) key zamana Mubarak mein mujhey ( kisi key girey huye) so Dinar miley they, chunanche mainey Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) sey masla daryaft kya to aap ney farmaya : eik saal tak unka aelan karo . mainey aelan kya to koi us raqam ko pehchan kar leney wala na mila . mainey phir Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) sey puchha to aap ney farmaya : uska aelan karo . main phir aelan karta raha lekin mujhey koi us raqam ko pehchan kar leney wala na mila . tab Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : uski thaili, bandhan aur tadaad yad rakho, phir eik saal tak aelan karo, agar koi us ko pehchanney wala aa gaya ( to theek) warna wo tumharey (doosrey) maal ki tarah (halal maal) hai."
2507,Hazrat Zaid bin Khalid Johni (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai ke Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) sey (kisi ki gum-shuda) uthai hui chiz key barey mein sawal kya gaya to aap ney farmaya : uska eik saal tak aelan kar. agar usey koi pehchan ley to wo usey dey dey . agar na pehchani jaey to uski thaili aur bandhan ki pehchan rakh aur usey istimal kar ley. (baad mein) agar uska Malik aa jaey to wo (raqam) usey ada kar dena .
2508,"Hazrat Zabaa bint Zuber Raziallahu anhu Alaiha ney Hazrat miqdaad bin Amr (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat bayan ki ke wo eik din qazaey-hajat key liye Baqee key qabristaan ki taraf gaey. (us zamaney mein) logon ki haalat ye thi ke aadmi do teen din main eik baar qazaey-hajat key liye jata. (tab bhi) is tarah mengniyan karta jis tarah oont mengniyan kartey hain. wo eik khandar mein chaley gaey. wo qazaey-hajat key liye bethey huye they ke eik chooha nazar aaya . usney bil mein sey eik Dinar nikala, phir bil mein gaya aur eik aur Dinar nikal laya yahan tak key usney (eik-eik kar key) satrah Dinar nikaley . phir eik surkh kapdey ka tukda nikal laya . Hazrat miqdaad kehtey hain : mainey kapdey ko utha kar dekha to mujhey is mein bhi eik Dinar mila . ye sab atthaara Dinar ho gaey . main unhen ley kar (khandar sey) bahar aa gaya aur unhen la kar Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ki khidmat mein pesh kar diya. aur un dinaron key milney ka waqia arz kya aur mainey kaha : aey Allah key Rasool! unki zakat ley lijiye . Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : unhen ley jao, un mein koi zakat nahin (kyonkey bees Dinar ka nisab pura nahin huwa.) Allah tujhey un mein barkat dey. phir farmaya : shayad tu ney bil mein haath dala hoga? mainey kaha : nahin, qism hai us zaat ki jisney aap ko haq key sath izzat bakhshi! Raavi ney kaha : un ki wafat tak wo Dinar khatam na huye ."
2509,"Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai, Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : madfun khazaney mein paanchwan hissa (zakat farz) hai."
2510,"Hazrat ibne-Abbas (Raziallahu anhuma) sey riwayat hai, Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : madfun khazaney mein paanchwan hissa (zakat) hai."
2511,"Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai, Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : tum sey pehley logon main eik aadmi tha, usney zamin khareedi to usey zamin mein soney ka bhara huwa eik maat (bada matka) mila . usney (bechney waley sey) kaha : mainey tujh sey zamin khareedi hai, sona nahin kharid . (isliye ye sona tum ley lo.) usney kaha : mainey tujhey zamin bechi aur jo kuch is mein tha (wo bhi sath hi bik gaya, isliye sona tumhara hai.) chunanche wo eik (teesrey) aadmi key paas apna muqadma ley gaey to usney kaha : kya tumhari koi aulad hai? eik ney kaha : mera eik ladka hai. aur doosrey ney kaha : meri eik ladki hai. us (faisla karney waley) ney kaha : ladkey ka nikah ladki sey kar do. wo dono us maal mein sey apni zaat par bhi kharch karen aur sadqa bhi karen ."
